<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-9970] Type argument inference does not work in closure</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-9970</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have the following Groovy program.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-groovy&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;Foo {}

final &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;A&amp;lt;T &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; Foo&amp;gt; {
  public T x;
  A(T x) {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.x = x;
  }
}

@groovy.transform.CompileStatic
public &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;C&amp;lt;T &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Number&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; {
  public void foo(T args) {
    final A&amp;lt;Foo&amp;gt; x = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; A&amp;lt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Foo()); &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// compiles
&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; closure = p -&amp;gt; {
        final A&amp;lt;Foo&amp;gt; y = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; A&amp;lt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Foo()); &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// does not compile
&lt;/span&gt;    }
  }
}

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;ActualBehavior&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Actual Behavior&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The program does not compile, and I get the following error.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
org.codehaus.groovy.control.MultipleCompilationErrorsException: startup failed:
Foo.groovy: 15: [Static type checking] - Cannot call A#&amp;lt;init&amp;gt;(T) with arguments [Foo]
 @ line 15, column 26.
           &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; A&amp;lt;Foo&amp;gt; y = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; A&amp;lt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Foo()); 
                            ^

1 error

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;ExpectedBehavior&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Expected Behavior&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Compile successfully.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;Comment&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Comment&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This should be a regression bug because it compiles with the 3.0.7 compiler and the 4.0.0-alpha-2.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;AffectedVersion&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Affected Version&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This programs fails when compiled with the compiler from the master (commit: 5d2944523f198d96b6515e85a24d2b4e43ce665f).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
